{"tid":1994701,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"楊明： 抹黑警隊唔公平,堅定撐警決心","createTime":"2020-04-29T16:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T17:19:24.000Z","uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"09ea3c7473034338cc79914be3a9b732c4f0239d","tid":1994701,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:12:50.000Z","msg":"戲里戲外撐警察 香港演員楊明：抹黑警隊不公平】近日，電視劇《機場特警》在港上映。主演之一楊明表示，自己從小就崇拜特警部隊，所以收到劇組邀請時非常興奮。在演藝生涯中多次扮演警察，讓楊明對警察的工作更加理解。自2019年6月香港爆發「修例風波」以來，楊明多次在公開場合勇敢發聲，支持警察，「去抹黑警隊對他們很不公平，他們為香港付出了很多。」為此，部分示威者在網上對楊明進行攻擊，還對其經營的店鋪進行打砸破壞和無理投訴，<span style=\"color: red;\">但這讓楊明更加堅定「撐警」的決心。</span><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://n.miaopai.com/media/JoGbF9b0qUDC4yiHIlA2uWmrSTaEjTtf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.miaopai.com%2Fmedia%2FJoGbF9b0qUDC4yiHIlA2uWmrSTaEjTtf&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=aa5393ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://n.miaopai.com/media/JoGbF9b0qUDC4yiHIlA2uWmrSTaEjTtf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f036d1a2451854b4083a548bb33ea41cf8875acd","tid":1994701,"uid":109713,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:13:46.000Z","msg":"唔需要抹 本身已經係黑晒"},{"pid":"c0d23846247aac7f1e97cdc98880f79acd8ce40d","tid":1994701,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:14:18.000Z","msg":"投訴佢發言令人不安 形象好唔點睇"},{"pid":"b5cfc7f47653f492ee69890af8e85ebf92afcef3","tid":1994701,"uid":114097,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:14:38.000Z","msg":"其身不正<br />\n撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef216f431ae7a6a7b0571db254e56695540f4126","tid":1994701,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:29:30.000Z","msg":"來來去去都係講呢d, 厭倦政府肉盾的回應<br />\n<br />\n你d業務恐怕經不起檢驗<br />\n<br />\n也經不起時間考驗"},{"pid":"d17365a10712954c587d95dafd922b1b8f333a6a","tid":1994701,"uid":16